      <br>• Battery runtime: 1-1.5 hours (vs 4-6 hours standard)
      <br>• Batteries needed: 6-8 per day (vs 2 per day normal)
      <br>• Battery replacement cost: RM50,000 annually (accelerated wear)
      <br>• Hydraulic repairs: RM30,000 annually (premature failure)
      <br>• Downtime: 20-30% (frequent breakdowns)
