      <br>• Fresh and frozen food delivery requires cold chain logistics
      <br>• Last-mile cold storage hubs expanding in urban areas
      <br>• Demand for frozen food warehousing increasing 20-25% annually</p>

      <h3>Export Market Growth</h3>

      <p>Malaysia frozen food exports growing:
      <br>• Seafood exports: +15% annually (require cold chain handling)
